OL,3,CSpygate: It's going to be a long
OL,4,Csummer for Saints' fans
OL,6,FSouthampton are appealing the decision
OL,7,Fto expel them from the Play-off Final.
OL,8,FChief Executive Phil Parsons calling
OL,9,Fthe sanction "manifestly
OL,10,Fdisproportionate to every previous
OL,11,Fsanction in the history of the game."
OL,13,FBut he starts his statement by
OL,14,Fapologising to "the Southampton
OL,15,Fsupporters whose extraordinary loyalty
OL,16,Fand support this season deserved
OL,17,Fbetter from the club."
OL,26,@qD@NOUsD@eO]vD@POUyD@VO]
