OL,3,CSpygate: It's going to be a long
OL,4,Csummer for Saints' fans
OL,6,FThat is what I want to talk about. The
OL,7,Fthousands of Southampton fans who
OL,8,Ftravel across the country to support
OL,9,Ftheir team.
OL,11,FOver 37,000 had snapped up tickets for
OL,12,FWembley. Myself and my sons among them.
OL,14,FThe Play-off Final two years ago was
OL,15,Fone of the best experiences of my
OL,16,Flife. Enjoying promotion with my boys.
OL,17,FSo we were all excitedly looking ahead
OL,18,Fto this Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
