OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779296759
OL,3,CSpygate: It's going to be a long
OL,4,Csummer for Saints' fans
OL,6,FInstead, it'll be an afternoon
OL,7,Favoiding the TV for me! Unless the
OL,8,Fappeal is successful and there's a
OL,9,Fremarkable turnaround.
OL,11,FI've spoken to plenty of other fans
OL,12,Fwho are equally upset, embarrassed,
OL,13,Fand ashamed by what's gone on. Many
OL,14,Fcalling for heads to roll at the club.
OL,16,FIt's going to be a long summer for
OL,17,FSaints' fans with players and staff
OL,18,Fpotentially leaving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
